data.description: Come and see this beautiful 177-acre Rock Water Ranch north of Rusk, Texas.  The high fence ranch is loaded with wildlife including Whitetail, Axis,  Fallow, Siki, Red Stag, Pere David, Aoudad, Texas Dall Ramm, Black Hawaiian Ram, Corsican Ram, Painted Desert Ram, and Wild Hogs.  It also features four ponds.  Rock Water Ranch features a 3200 Sq Ft Lodge with four bedrooms and two baths with the capacity to house 24.  It also has a Tiny House of 394 sq ft which is currently used for the Ranch Manager's quarters.  You will find all the equipment you need for business or commercial hunts or for personal pleasure in the 3 storage buildings (10x20) and a barn (30x40).  The Ranch comes equipped with meat processing equipment and an 80 lb ice maker You will find that Rock Water Ranch can offer a country club experience to your hunting vacation stay.
